# LucidGate example list: exceptioncookiephraselist
# Format: One cookie phrase per line. Use name= or a distinctive value fragment.
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# tracking_id=
# session_debug=
# unsafe_consent=1
# ad_profile=
# risk_marker=high
# legacy_token=
# xleak=
# analytics_id=
# experiment_unsafe=
# thirdparty_id=
